## Key Decisions

| Decision | Choice | Rationale |
|----------|--------|-----------|
| Bucket duration | 100ms | Balance responsiveness vs overhead |
| Rollback window | 200ms (2 buckets) | GGPO-style bounded divergence |
| Entity ordering | By ID | Consistent conflict resolution |
| Timeout handling | Proceed with partial data | Accept divergence, don't block |
| Math library | StrictMath | Per-platform consistency |
| Force accumulation | Reduction tree | Stable floating-point |

